An understanding of Server/Client based software and relational databases.

  * Sound knowledge of Microsoft SQL Server including understanding SQL related queries. 
  * Experience in a ** software ** support role. It doesnâ€™t have to be in the IT, Automotive or Tyre industry, although either would be an advantage. Mostly, you must have the desire to help people. 
